---
const steps = [
  {
    n: '01',
    title: 'Read the wrist',
    body:
      'The Apple Watch streams accelerometer, gyroscope, and attitude data — three signals that together describe how your wrist moves through space.',
  },
  {
    n: '02',
    title: 'Match the signature',
    body:
      'Every exercise has a distinct motion. A sit-up tilts the watch through 60°. A push-up rotates the wrist 20°. A squat sends a clean acceleration pulse at the bottom and the top.',
  },
  {
    n: '03',
    title: 'Count the rep',
    body:
      'A different detector for each exercise watches its signature in real time. Cross the threshold, the count ticks up. Cross back, it arms again. No cloud round-trip.',
  },
];
---

<section id="how" class="section bg-[var(--card-soft)]">
  <div class="container-page">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-4">How it works</p>
      <h2 class="h2 mb-4">Sensors, not guesses.</h2>
      <p class="lede">
        No camera. No cloud ML. Just the same motion sensors Apple ships in every Watch,
        read with a different detector for each exercise.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ol class="mt-14 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3" role="list">
      {
        steps.map((step) => (
          <li class="card relative h-full">
            <span class="text-gradient text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.18em]">
              {step.n}
            </span>
            <h3 class="h3 mt-3">{step.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--fg-muted)]">
              {step.body}
            </p>
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ol>

    <div
      class="mx-auto mt-10 flex max-w-3xl flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--card)] px-6 py-4 text-sm text-[var(--fg-muted)]"
    >
      <span><strong class="text-[var(--fg)]">Sensitivity slider</strong> 1–10 per exercise</span>
      <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <span><strong class="text-[var(--fg)]">Live diagnostics</strong> on the Watch</span>
      <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <span><strong class="text-[var(--fg)]">No black box</strong> — see what's detecting</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
